<!-- Node: "DOOM 3 at QuakeCon!!" -->
<div class="body_box_header">DOOM 3 at QuakeCon!!</div>
<div class="body_box"><small>Submitted by <a href="http://www.gamedesign.net/user/view/2157" title="View user profile.">Method</a> on Tuesday, July 6, 2004 - 18:32</small><br /><br />
