<!-- Node: "3D Realms is hiring" -->
<div class="body_box_header">3D Realms is hiring</div>
<div class="body_box"><small>Submitted by <a href="http://www.gamedesign.net/user/view/2157" title="View user profile.">Method</a> on Monday, June 28, 2004 - 01:33</small><br /><br />
<a href = "http://www.3drealms.com/">3D Realms</a> is looking for a Level Designer. This is a full time position with relocation to Garland, Texas. Head over to <a href = "http://www.3drealms.com/gethired.html#available">3D Realms</a> to check out the job requirements and benifits.
<br /><br />
