<!-- Node: "New DOOM 3 release date?" -->
<div class="body_box_header">New DOOM 3 release date?</div>
<div class="body_box"><small>Submitted by <a href="http://www.gamedesign.net/user/view/2157" title="View user profile.">Method</a> on Wednesday, June 23, 2004 - 15:59</small><br /><br />
It seems now that some of the retailers switched their release date for DOOM 3 to August 3rd 2004. So let's hope this is the final release date and we get to play DOOM 3 this summer. You can read more on <a href = "http://www.planetdoom.com/">PlanetDOOM</a>.
